				<td valign="top"><h1>Services &amp Amenities</h1>	
				
				<h2>Luxury San Francisco Hotel Accommodations</h2>
				
				<font class="text" color="#ffffff" face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="2">Located on the Embarcadero near the Financial District, the Harbor Court Hotel offers exceptional services and amenities, making our boutique hotel an inviting destination for business and leisure travelers alike. Our San Francisco luxury hotel features energy and style, along with welcome conveniences and an ideal location for venturing out to the Embarcadero or the San Francisco Ferry Building.<br /><br />
				
				The Harbor Court Hotel, a Kimpton Hotel, offers luxury San Francisco accommodations, including the following services and amenities:
				
				<ul>
				    <li>Personalized room preferences and welcome amenities for 
					<a href="http://www.kimptonintouch.com" target="_blank">Kimpton InTouch guest loyalty</a> members</li>
					<li>Complimentary wireless Internet access (WiFi) throughout the hotel lobby</li>
					<li>Complimentary weekday morning town car service within the Financial District and SOMA</li>
					<li>Complimentary Equator Coffee (Organic &amp; Fair Trade) and Mighty Leaf Teas available each morning in our living room </li>
					<li>Complimentary manager's wine reception each evening by our living room fireplace</li>
					<li>Overnight valet/laundry service available</li>
					<li>Valet Parking is available for $35 plus tax overnight with in-and-out privileges</li>
					<li>Complimentary use of state-of-the-art health facility with Olympic-sized swimming pool, located next door to the hotel</li>
					<li>Professional meeting space available</li>
					<li>Business services available, including photocopying and typing services</li>
					<li>Room service</li>
					<li>We are a pet-friendly hotel</li>
					<li>Adjacent to the hotel is <a href="http://www.ozumo.com/" onclick="NewWindow(this.href,'name','790','600','yes','1','0','1');return false">Ozumo Sushi Bar and Robata Grill</a>, serving exceptional Japanese cuisine, and the Sumo Lounge cocktail bar, featuring exotic sake</li>
                    <li>Complimentary use of state-of-the-art health facility with Olympic-sized swimming pool, located next door to the hotel</li>
				</ul>
				
				<b><a href="http://ymcasf.org/" onclick="NewWindow(this.href,'name','790','600','yes','1','0','1');return false">Embarcadero YMCA</a></b><br />
				Guests of the downtown Harbor Court Hotel can take full advantage of the Embarcadero YMCA, a state-of-the-art health facility right next door to the hotel. Described as one of the top ten hotel health clubs in the country by <em>Fitness Magazine</em>, the Embarcadero YMCA features:
				<ul>
					<li>An Olympic-sized indoor swimming pool (with water aerobics classes offered daily)</li>
					<li>Racquetball and basketball courts, a full gymnasium and rooftop jogging track</li>
					<li>Pilates, yoga, spinning and kickboxing classes offered on a weekly basis (no additional charge)</li>
					<li>20 Stairmasters, 30 Lifecycles, 10 treadmills, plus Nautilus, Cybex and free weight equipment</li>
					<li>Men's and women's steam room, sauna and Jacuzzi with full locker room facilities</li>
					<li>An expertly trained staff</li>
					<li>Babysitting services</li>
					<li>Open Monday through Friday, 5:30 a.m. to 10 p.m., Saturday, 8 a.m. to 8 p.m., and Sunday, 9 a.m. to 6 p.m.</li>
				</ul>
				</font></td>
			</tr>
